                                <item xml:id="e3">
                                    <locus target="#2 #4"/>
                                    <desc type="CommemorativeNote">contain a notice of the death by violence of 
                                        <persName ref="PRS12570Niqolawos">
                                 <roleName type="title">ʾabbā</roleName>Niqolāwos</persName>, 
                                        <persName ref="PRS12571Asfakresto">
                                 <roleName type="title">ʾabbā</roleName>ʾAṣfa Krǝstos</persName>,
                                        <persName ref="PRS12572Awsegnyos">
                                 <roleName type="title">ʾabbā</roleName>ʾAwsǝgnyos</persName>
                                        and others on the 3rd of Miyāziyā with account of events connected therewith in the reigns of  <persName ref="PRS10375Yohanne">Yoḥannǝs I</persName>,
                                        <persName ref="PRS5616IyasuI">ʾIyāsu I</persName> and <persName ref="PRS2377Bakaffa">Bakaffā</persName> in whose reign this page seems to have been written.</desc>
                                    
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="e4">
